reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Price is right
reviews.reviewText: The price is right, the colors are pretty, the length is great, they are made well and they don’t catch on fire… yet lolI always catch these on sale and buy a bunch.In my house of 2 adults, 4 kids and a lot of electronic crap… we go through some chargers. So far none of these have died and I purchased our first ones back in April 2023. The reason I have to buy more is because my kids steal them, then lose them or give them to their friends (if you ask them these are all lies) 🤣🙄They charge quick, don’t make your things overheat and none of the braiding has torn or come away from the wires.You can’t go wrong and you’ll pay twice as much for one crappy one at the gas station next time you’re in a bind, so might as well and throw one in your console.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 9, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I purchased these at Christmas time for stocking stuffers. I made sure to purchase the multi-color pack so that the kids can identify their charging cords. Now, there is no fighting over the cords or cubes. At 6 feet long this a great cord to use on your nightstand or a couch that is far away from an outlet. A great reasonably priced gift for kids, co-workers and friends. Everyone needs charging cords!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars 1 year life maybe , shortages , short survival , otherwise good
reviews.reviewText: They were decent charger cords. Out of the four, only 2 still work. I’ve had them for just over a year. The two that still work are the ones that stay at my job and the one in my car. The one in my house and the travel cord shorted out pretty quickly.Given the price the chargers are fine. They work exactly as they’re supposed to. Colors are pretty .

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Didn’t last a year
reviews.reviewText: For the price, this is probably to be expected but if you’re looking for long lasting quality this isn’t it. By May 2023, one year since buying, every cord has stopped working. Some lasting longer than others but none making it to the post 1 year mark. Cheap enough that they don’t get a 1 star review because of this but I wouldn’t really recommend buying if you have other options.
